idy up the CRA boilerplate, add Tailwind CSS so the TodoList actually looks decent, and then walk through deploying the whole thing to GitHub Pages step by step. By the end you'll have a real, shareable URL for your TodoList.","md","en",{},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002Flearn-react-21-cra-todolist-github-pages","7",{"title":6,"description":1635},false,"en\u002FReact\u002Flearn-react-21-cra-todolist-github-pages",[1645,1646,1647,1648,1649,1553,1591,1586],"You'll Learn React Eventually, So Why Not Now?","React Basics","TodoList","Create React App","CRA",null,"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F05\u002Flearn-react-21-cra-todolist-github-pages\u002F","SjTVMN2dSGsD_4waFMVtm37xydq0GfA3UwjrrYe8B10",{"newer":1654,"older":1658},{"url":1655,"title":1656,"date":1657},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F06\u002Freact-day-22-vite-setup\u002F","React, You'll Learn It Eventually — Why Not Now? - Setting Up React with Vite - (22)","2022-10-06 00:00:01",{"url":1659,"title":1660,"date":1661},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F04\u002Freact-day-20-strictmode-and-web-vitals\u002F","React, Might As Well Learn It Now - StrictMode and Web Vitals in CRA (20)","2022-10-04 00:00:01",[1663,1668,1673],{"url":1664,"title":1665,"date":1666,"readingMinutes":1667},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F14\u002Flearn-react-now-30-wrap-up-and-toc\u002F","Learn React Now — Wrap-up Notes & Full Table of Contents (30)","2022-10-14 00:00:01","4",{"url":1669,"title":1670,"date":1671,"readingMinutes":1672},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F13\u002Flearn-react-29-react-redux-quick-start\u002F","Learn React Eventually, So Why Not Now? - React Redux: Redux and a Quick Start - (29)","2022-10-13 00:00:01","6",{"url":1674,"title":1675,"date":1676,"readingMinutes":1667},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F12\u002Freact-day-28-router-lazy-loading\u002F","Why Learn React Eventually? Learn It Now! - React Router Lazy Loading (28)","2022-10-12 00:00:01",1784013072866]